## Interaction Contract

- The modal overlay exposes `role="dialog"` and `aria-modal="true"`; when `title` is provided, an instance-scoped `aria-labelledby` links to the title.
- Opening focuses the overlay root; hiding or unmounting restores the previously focused element.
- Backdrop click, Escape, and close button dismissal emit `update:modelValue(false)` and `close`.
- `TModal` is the lightweight current entry backed by `TxModal`; when no `header/footer` slot is provided it does not override title or footer behavior.

